18#include "tools.h"
19
20int dumpconfig(struct cmd_context *cmd, int argc, char **argv)
21{
22 const char *file = arg_str_value(cmd, file_ARG, NULL);
23
24 if (!write_config_file(cmd->cft, file, argc, argv)) {
25 stack;
26 return ECMD_FAILED;
27 }
28
29 return ECMD_PROCESSED;
30}
